Rise Fanzin Monu Bot Privacy Policy
Last Updated: 20.02.2024

Welcome to Rise Fanzin Monu Bot!

This Privacy Policy outlines how Rise Fanzin Monu Bot collects and uses information solely for the purpose of bot functionality.

1. Information We Collect

User-Provided Information: We collect information you provide while using the Bot, limited to text commands, user IDs, and server information.

Automatically Collected Information: Certain information, like IP addresses, device details, and usage data, may be collected automatically.

2. How We Use Your Information

We use collected information for:

Providing and maintaining the Bot.
Improving Bot functionality and user experience.
Responding to user inquiries and providing support.
Detecting, preventing, and addressing technical issues.
3. Data Sharing and Security

Third-Party Services: Some user information may be accessible to third-party services assisting with Bot operation.

Security: While we take reasonable measures to protect collected information, complete security during internet transmission or electronic storage cannot be guaranteed.

4. User Control and Opt-Out

Data Access and Deletion: Users can request data access or deletion by contacting us at bitter@riseonline.com.tr.

Opt-Out: Users can opt-out of providing certain information, but this might affect Bot functionality.

5. Changes to This Privacy Policy

This Privacy Policy may be updated. The date of the latest revision will be indicated at the document's top.

6. Contact Us

If you have questions, contact us at bitter@riseonline.com.tr.
